permissions.Name: User.ReadBasic.All
permissions.Description: Read all users' basic profiles
permissions.FullDescription: Allows the app to read a basic set of profile properties of other users in your organization on your behalf. Includes display name, first and last name, email address and photo.

permissions.Name: User.Read.All
permissions.Description: Read all users' full profiles
permissions.FullDescription: Allows the app to read the full set of profile properties, reports, and managers of other users in your organization, on your behalf.

permissions.Name: Directory.ReadWrite.All
permissions.Description: Read and write directory data
permissions.FullDescription: Allows the app to read and write data in your organization's directory, such as other users, groups.  It does not allow the app to delete users or groups, or reset user passwords.

permissions.FullDescription: Allows the app to read data in your organization's directory.

permissions.Name: DeviceManagementManagedDevices.ReadWrite.All
permissions.Description: Read and write Microsoft Intune devices

permissions.Name: DeviceManagementManagedDevices.Read.All
permissions.Description: Read Microsoft Intune devices
permissions.FullDescription: Allows the app to read the properties of devices managed by Microsoft Intune, without a signed-in user.

permissions.Description: Read and write Microsoft Intune device configuration and policies
permissions.FullDescription: Allows the app to read and write properties of Microsoft Intune-managed device configuration and device compliance policies and their assignment to groups, without a signed-in user.

permissions.Name: DeviceManagementConfiguration.Read.All
permissions.Description: Read Microsoft Intune device configuration and policies
permissions.FullDescription: Allows the app to read properties of Microsoft Intune-managed device configuration and device compliance policies and their assignment to groups, without a signed-in user.

permissions.Name: DeviceManagementApps.ReadWrite.All
permissions.Description: Read and write Microsoft Intune apps
permissions.FullDescription: Allows the app to read and write the properties, group assignments and status of apps, app configurations and app protection policies managed by Microsoft Intune, without a signed-in user.

permissions.Name: DeviceManagementApps.Read.All
